               <code code="42232-9" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="PRECAUTIONS SECTION"/>
               <title>Precautions</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Federal (U.S.A.) Law prohibits dispensing without prescription.  Store at controlled room temperature 68º - 77º F (20ºC - 25ºC). <br/>
